node.text: Friends and family from Revive, Force and 3Block have a long session at shredquarters in one day.

node.text: This is a shirt with the word “kickflip” on it because kickflips are cool. Pick it up today on @theshredquarters! Link in bio as well. Featuring @johnhill 📸: @daniel.hare #reviveskateboards #kickflipsarecool #soisthisshirt #coolflipscoolshirts
